msgctxt "1558	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta follow the river to avoid gettin' lost. Have to hurry before the cold gets me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1643	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There's a bear nearby. Gotta follow the river and find Baba-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1709	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Baba-chan could be in trouble. Better hurry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1754	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta get a rabbit to nurse Baba back to health."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1803	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han's supposed to be close. Guess I should go deeper."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1865	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han says it's important. Gotta crouch and make sure I ain't seen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1939	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta reload to use the gun. Let's give it a go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1988	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta nail the boulder across the stream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2030	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Off to find that huntin' hut. I should check the map to avoid gettin' lost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2106	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Look for deer tracks, huh? Should be some right around here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2167	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta follow the deer tracks. They'll lead me to my prey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2225	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I'll crouch down to sneak up on deer. Gotta hunt to survive on the mountain, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2309	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Time to collect the deer I shot. Can't waste the life they gave up for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2384	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Back to the village. Gotta repay Nishina-han's wife for the favor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2451	EXPLANATION"
msgid "After returning the favor, I'll head over to Okudera-han and learn to trap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2527	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta go up along the river and look for trap sites."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2580	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Set a trap at that trap site there, huh? Sounds easy enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2641	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There should be other trap sites here. I should find 'em with a quick look around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2724	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There should be one more trap site here. Gotta find it somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2788	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I set traps at the trap sites around here. Guess I'll go check if anything's been caught yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2882	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yama-oroshi! Here!? I gotta chase it away from the village!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2942	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Two choices. Leave for Tsukimino now, or stay here to hunt a while longer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3017	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Nishina-han and another guy haven't come back from the mountain yet..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3088	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Nishina-han hasn't returned from the mountain. I should check on his wife."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3163	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Nishina-han's wife is worried. Gotta tell Okudera-han and, then go find these people."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3249	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta find some sort of a clue. Guess I'll just hike around till I find one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3326	EXPLANATION"
msgid "These footprints should lead me to Nishina-han or the lost guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3390	EXPLANATION"
msgid "This guy's gonna need food."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3418	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The mountain's a rough place. I gotta be tougher to survive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3479	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There's a stranger at the village entrance. Sakurai-han seemed concerned, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3558	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi's after Yama-oroshi as well. Better let Okudera-han know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3623	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That blast had to be Narumi's doin'. Gotta go deeper and find him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3690	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi's gotta be close. Let's follow the footprints from the blast site."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3764	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That Narumi better not cause any trouble. Not gonna lie, I'm worried."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3834	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han's sick. Gotta check on him..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3876	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I gotta get bear bile for Okudera-han. Need to get ready and tell Sakurai-han before I head out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3973	EXPLANATION"
msgid "First, I gotta find some bear tracks. Gotta make sure the cold doesn't do me in, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4059	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Follow the bear tracks, and I'll find a bear. Can't lose sight of these tracks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4139	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Bears could be in the area. Gotta be careful."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4185	EXPLANATION"
msgid "This area seems to be the bear's territory. I'll find it and get the bile I need."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4267	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Managed to take that bear down. Just need the bile, and to give thanks for it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4346	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han's condition's settled, but what'll I do from here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4409	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi scattered bear bait across the mountain. Gotta tell Sakurai-han when I can go get them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4504	EXPLANATION"
msgid "There's supposed to be around eight pieces of bear bait scattered around. Gotta go on foot and find 'em."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4609	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Found one. Seven left. Got a long ways to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4655	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That's the second one. Six more bear bait pieces to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4711	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That's the third. Where are the other five pieces?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4762	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Four found. Halfway there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4789	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Finally. That's five. Three more to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4829	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That's six recovered, two more to go. Not much left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4882	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That's seven . Just one left to find. Gotta keep at it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4938	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Got all the bear bait, but that gunfire's worryin'. Better check it out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5011	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi might be where he was before. Let's track his footprints."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5076	EXPLANATION"
msgid "I can't kill Yama-oroshi now. Gotta beat it down off the mountain!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5143	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Made it off the mountain, but just barely. Did Narumi make it down safe?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5216	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi's not back from the mountain. Gotta tell Sakurai-han and rescue Narumi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5295	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta head to where Yama-oroshi appeared. Should be some clues there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5365	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi might still be alive. Gotta follow this blood trail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5425	EXPLANATION"
msgid "That's a lot of blood. Gotta hurry. Narumi might be bleedin' out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5491	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta get Narumi to the village. Despite all he's done, I ain't lettin' him die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5572	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Not far to the village now. Gotta get there before Narumi drops dead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5642	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Narumi went off to a hospital in town. Okudera-han's condition is worryin' me, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5729	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han's better. What a relief. Gotta get ready to shoot Yama-oroshi with a transmitter shot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5828	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta find Yama-oroshi with nothin' to go on. Maybe I'll head to mid-mountain as a start."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5918	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Shootin' the back or legs is no good. Gotta plug it right in the belly. I'll take the shot when it stands!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6025	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Got the transmitter planted. Mission accomplished. Back to the village."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6097	EXPLANATION"
msgid "We know where Yama-oroshi is. Gotta get ready to go up with Okudera-han."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6170	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yama-oroshi's location is on the map. We'll use that to chase it down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6241	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yama-oroshi's movin' deeper into the wild. Gotta rely on this signal and chase it down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6329	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It's going even deeper? Well, we just gotta keep chasin' it this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6399	EXPLANATION"
msgid "It's still goin' deeper up the mountain. Gotta be careful while chasin' the signal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6483	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yama-oroshi's across the canyon. Even Okudera-han can't do a thing about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6562	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han went up by himself. The man's still too weak for that. I gotta help him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6647	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Okudera-han's been up there a long while. I'll go deeper and find the man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6722	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Nishina-han said he had somethin' to show me at his place..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6783	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Nishina-han's in his storage shed. What's he want to show me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6845	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta settle things with Yama-oroshi. Time to get geared up at Okudera-han's and go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6930	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yama-oroshi should be around here. Gotta stay alert..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6985	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Time to settle score. This is one fight I can't lose!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7039	EXPLANATION"
msgid "The gun's useless! Nothin' to do but slug it out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7089	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Gotta pick off all three, nice and neat. Concentrate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7143	EXPLANATION"
msgid "Yama-oroshi won't come down near the village again. I should visit Okudera-han now and then."
msgstr ""

